   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_1_00024"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich.
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">I. Wollzeile 15</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_1_00026"/><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute> we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>s Ihnen nicht
               unangenehm,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chicken Sie mir noch heut wenig<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens
               100 Cigaretten<unclear>.</unclear> –</p><p>Ich bin heut bei der <rs ref="#pmb30593" type="work">Braut v Messina</rs>, da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>, wahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinl. mit <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Hugo</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb1106" type="place">Resid-Hotel</rs>. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb819" type="place">Pucher</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
